Description of City JazzFest:  This full day music fest will feature Jeff Lorber, Spyro Gyra, Marc Antoine and the headlining package, Dave Koz & Friends including Michael McDonald, Brian Culbertson and Norman Brown. The show is produced by House Of Blues Concerts.  An intimate concert setting has been developed at PGE Park that will feel like a small amphitheatre, but with all the new amenities PGE Park has to offer.